episodes.title: A Nutritionist’s Honest Take on Diet Cults by Matt Fitzgerald
episodes.description:
As a certified nutritionist who’s lived through chronic gut issues, I had high hopes for Diet Cults by Matt Fitzgerald. Here’s my honest, no-fluff review—what the book gets right, where it misses the mark, and how to find freedom from food dogma.

Book link: https://www.amazon.com/Diet-Cults-Surprising-Fallacy-Nutrition/dp/1605985600/ref=tmm_hrd_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&dib_tag=se&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.ATip7MWDNypeUXAIhbwqScwvK6rJwMkgG6QuNN6HtsGwGNPCOMBwmx6N8xniev8AwIAJ9xtIqHWvnc4ERbQDo__2jWNFmPRtb2-Vf0n2ecetsbjQvIvcajYryTjUh8om.1WD8GKZhQxaQ7bX5d-0LzenFqCCV26sV9xFEObk_E7Q&qid=1759063248&sr=8-1
